; Regression test for issue #797: Setting precision on the command line (BZ#797)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/797
;
; The D directive in the journal sets display precision for amounts.
; This test verifies that the D directive correctly controls the number of
; decimal places shown in register output.

D $1,000.00

2024/01/01 Coffee Shop
    Expenses:Food    $10.1234
    Assets:Checking

test reg
24-Jan-01 Coffee Shop           Expenses:Food                $10.12       $10.12
                                Assets:Checking             $-10.12            0
end test

; Also verify that higher precision can be set via D directive
; (amounts with fewer decimal places are padded out)

test reg --format "%(scrub(amount))\n"
$10.12
$-10.12
end test
